{
  "stem": "6845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he's the one who told to Nick that, look, I want you and your family to go up in the mountains as a certain kind of physician.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I want you to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's-- would be a good idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we never dreamed why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But once we left, we realized, just very quickly, that this was definitely a lifesaving suggestion or plan that-- to send us up there because the ghetto got organized, or started to function, like, three days after we left.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they started to carry in the people and amongst the first was my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my mother was besides herself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And yes, we did agree that we would go up to that place in the hills-- I should say, hills.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's like here, the Appalachian, kind of similar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to go with an ox cart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We knew it would be as primitive as it could be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But Nick and I felt if the governor is trying to give us this chance, you shouldn't just take it lightly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother said, no way, she wouldn't come with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she-- and my brother was married, meantime, my older brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was married, and they had a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So my mother was, of course, involved also with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, anyway, we went up to the hill country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And supposedly, it was an epidemic of thyroid or typhus-- thyroid?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, thyroid is not-- Typhoid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some very meager accommodations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, anyway, we took with us some cash money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took some jewelry with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we did because, at that point, everywhere is afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
